{"title":"CSS —— 布局","date":"2019-11-23T09:01:58.812Z","thumbnail":"https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/11/23/MbXs5q.md.jpg","link":"2019/11/23/CSS-layout","updated":"2019-11-25T02:21:14.517Z","content":"<h2 id=\"盒模型\">盒模型<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#盒模型\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li><p>标准盒模型</p>\n<p>width = content</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>IE盒模型</p>\n<p>width = content + border + padding</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"position\">position<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#position\"></a></h2><p>static | absolute | relative | fixed</p>\n<p>absolute和fixed是脱离文档流的</p>\n<p>absolute相对于父级最近的absolute和relative发生偏移</p>\n<p>后三者可以设置z-index</p>\n<h2 id=\"常用布局方式\">常用布局方式<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#常用布局方式\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li>table表格布局</li>\n<li>float浮动 + margin</li>\n<li>inline-box 布局</li>\n<li>flexbox布局</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"table布局\">table布局<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#table布局\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li>直接使用表格进行布局</li>\n<li>使用div进行模拟，<code>display：table</code>，<code>display：table-row</code>，<code>display：table-cell</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"flexbox布局\">flexbox布局<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#flexbox布局\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li><p>弹性盒子</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>盒子原本就是并列的</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2015/07/flex-grammar.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">更多</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"float布局（最常用）\">float布局（最常用）<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#float布局（最常用）\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"float\">float<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#float\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li><p>脱离文档流（不会对其他元素的布局产生影响）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>不脱离文本流（会影响其他文字的排布）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>对自己的影响:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>形成块(BFC)</li>\n<li>位置尽量靠上</li>\n<li>位置尽量靠左(右)，在尽量靠上的前提下</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>对兄弟的影响</p>\n<ul>\n<li>上面贴非float元素</li>\n<li>旁边贴float元素</li>\n<li>不影响其他块级元素的位置</li>\n<li>影响其他块级元素的内部文本</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>对父级元素的影响</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>从布局上消失</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>高度塌陷 </p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>塌陷元素设置overflow: auto | hidden</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>加伪元素</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">.xxx::after&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  clear:both;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  display: block;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  height:0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  visibility:hidden;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"经典布局\">经典布局<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#经典布局\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>两栏布局</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  height: 500px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  width: 100%;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.left</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  float: left;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  width: 200px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  height: 100%;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  background: gray;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.right</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  height: 100%;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  margin-left: 200px;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-tag\">background</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:hotpink</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"left\"</span>&gt;</span>左<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"right\"</span>&gt;</span>右<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<ul>\n<li>三栏布局</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.container</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    height: 500px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    width: 100%;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.left</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    float: left;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    width: 200px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    height: 100%;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    background: gray;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.middle</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    height: 100%;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    margin-left: 200px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    margin-right: 200px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    background: khaki;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">  <span class=\"selector-class\">.right</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    float: right;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    width: 200px;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    height: 100%;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"selector-tag\">background</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:hotpink</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"container\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"left\"</span>&gt;</span>左<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"right\"</span>&gt;</span>右<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span> <span class=\"attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"middle\"</span>&gt;</span>中<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"inline-block\">inline-block<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#inline-block\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li>像文本一样去排block元素</li>\n<li>没有清除浮动等问题</li>\n<li>需要处理间歇<ul>\n<li>父元素字体大小设置为0；子元素中再设置字体大小</li>\n<li>将两个inline-box的div间的换行注释或者删除</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"响应式设计和布局\">响应式设计和布局<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#响应式设计和布局\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li><p>在不同设备间正常使用</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>一般主要处理屏幕大小问题</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>主要办法：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>隐藏 + 折行 + 自适应空间</li>\n<li>rem/viewport/media query</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>技巧：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@media (xxx){}，注意范围大的放前面</li>\n<li>设置固定viewport宽度，以适应不同手机的显示</li>\n<li>rem，注意rem会出现不精确的问题</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"面试题\">面试题<a href=\"2019/11/23/CSS-layout#面试题\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li>实现两栏/三栏布局</li>\n<li>postion:abosolute/fxed的区别</li>\n<li>dispaly: inline-box的间隙<ul>\n<li>原因：字符间距</li>\n<li>解决：消灭字符或者消灭间距</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>如何清除浮动</li>\n<li>如何适配移动端页面</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"CSS —— 效果","link":"2019/11/25/CSS-effect"},"next":{"title":"CSS —— 基础","link":"2019/11/22/CSS-base"},"plink":"http://allenxz.github.io/2019/11/23/CSS-layout/","toc":[{"title":"盒模型","id":"盒模型","index":"1"},{"title":"position","id":"position","index":"2"},{"title":"常用布局方式","id":"常用布局方式","index":"3","children":[{"title":"table布局","id":"table布局","index":"3.1"},{"title":"flexbox布局","id":"flexbox布局","index":"3.2"},{"title":"float布局（最常用）","id":"float布局（最常用）","index":"3.3","children":[{"title":"float","id":"float","index":"3.3.1"},{"title":"经典布局","id":"经典布局","index":"3.3.2"}]},{"title":"inline-block","id":"inline-block","index":"3.4"}]},{"title":"响应式设计和布局","id":"响应式设计和布局","index":"4"},{"title":"面试题","id":"面试题","index":"5"}]}